<ab facs="#facs_121_r3l32">als das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt / . Das wöllen wir vmb ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r3l33">erſamen <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in <expan>ſölıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒü <expan>allencʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_121_r3l34">mit wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Vrba<ex>n</ex>ȷ</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_121" id="60r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
