<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                        Wilhalm Rumel und <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pirkheim<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie sie czü ew gen
                            <expan>Straszb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und <add>do</add> fürbas durch
                        czefüren geschicket <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lxiiii secke englischer
                        wöllen, der in gefüret <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hans
                                <expan>Slat<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Costencz xlviii seck und Chuncz
                                <expan>Prag<ex>er</ex></expan> xvi <expan>sekk</expan>, da von der
                        czollner bey ew czol <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab, das sünderlich
                                <expan>czügange<ex>n</ex></expan> sey,
                                <add><expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan></add> daz
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Hans <expan>Slat<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht
                        weste, daz wir und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey ew czolfrey sein.
                        Nu sind <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lxiiii secke wollen halb des
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Wilhalm Rumels und halb des
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pirkheim<ex>ers</ex></expan> und <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gesellscheft, auch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, als sie die bede vor uns czü den
                                <expan>heilige<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt und gesworn
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz die ir und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein awsman
                                <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemain daran nicht hab.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>czolln<ex>er</ex></expan> reden und bestellen wöllet, daz er den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den czol widergeb und es fürbas gen
                        den <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey ew</add> halt, als das
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Das wöllen wir umb ewr ersamen
                                <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in
                            <expan>sölich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czü <expan>allenczeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit
                        willen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
